Challenge_6 - solution
#given list to swap
mylist = [1, 2, 3, 4]

# to swap first and last items 
#using temp var #Begineer
"""temp = mylist[0]
mylist[0] = mylist[-1]
mylist[-1] = temp

print(mylist)"""

# using swap easy pytonic way (it is something oly python allows)
mylist[0], mylist[-1] = mylist[-1], mylist[0] # simple and Best

print(mylist)
